com.revature.Services

Interface Authenticate

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AuthenticateUser

    public interface Authenticate
    A user authentication service.

    The Authenticate interface provides methods that authenticate users (whether they are a customers or employees).

    The Authenticate interface also provides methods for getting and returning Employee objects and Customer objects (by using usernames).

    Author:
    josecanela
